text: Federico Páez Chiriboga (4 June 1877 - 9 February 1974) was President of Ecuador from September 26, 1935 through October 23, 1937. He died on 9 February 1974 in Quito, Ecuador from natural causes. He was 96 years old. ==References== Category:1876 births Category:1974 deaths Category:Presidents of Ecuador Category:Sportspeople from Quito
title: Federico Páez
